        {
            "title": "WeChat Pay HK夥深圳南山 派千萬消費券",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>為配合北上消費，騰訊（00700）旗下WeChat Pay HK宣布與深圳市南山區商務局合作舉辦「2026年南山區入境<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"消費券\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:消費券;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/消費券\">消費券</a>活動」，預計向WeChat Pay HK用戶提供總值逾千萬港元的消費券，首輪派發將於4月1日至6月30日進行，涵蓋熱門餐飲、零售及海岸城商圈等，消費滿指定金額可享四折優惠。</span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>首輪4．1開鑼 可享四折優惠</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">騰訊金融科技副總裁洪丹毅表示，今年前兩個月WeChat Pay HK用戶在內地消費筆數相比去年同期接近翻倍，預期勢頭持續至4月，倘有消費券加持，相信覆蓋的商戶銷量可進一步增長。本次消費券活動料能吸引更多人流流向南山區商圈，從而帶動交易量增長。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ab96f37d-b228-31d6-b7b4-abd4eca22540-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">WeChat Pay HK用戶透過「內地游」頁面進入活動專頁，可點擊領取消費券，設有餐飲、零售、南山海岸城商圈指定商戶及南山區指定商戶4個類別消費券，例如餐飲消費券滿100減60元、滿500減300元等，零售消費券滿800減480元等。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">針對用戶交通出行需要，WeChat Pay HK同時推出多項乘車及召車優惠，分別聯同環島中港通提供前往深圳灣口岸直通巴士半價優惠券；以及與滴滴出行發放價值高達100元無門檻香港召車立減券（適用於目的地為深圳灣口岸訂單），及低至六折內地召車優惠券（適用於目的地為南山區的訂單）。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/wechat-pay-hk%E5%A4%A5%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8D%97%E5%B1%B1-%E6%B4%BE%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E5%88%B8-181300364.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-25 02:20:27",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "泡泡瑪特今放榜 股價料區間上落",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"泡泡瑪特\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:泡泡瑪特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/泡泡瑪特\">泡泡瑪特</a>（09992）今日公布2025年業績，摩根士丹利表示，由於市場觀點高度分化，預計泡泡瑪特股價於今日發布業績後將保持波動，可能先上漲，然後進入新一輪區間震盪。泡泡瑪特股價昨升7.4%，收報217.2元。</span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大摩報告指出，泡泡瑪特過去兩個半月股價顯著波動，但未觀察到看好或看淡雙方對盈利預期發生實質性改變。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>大摩：市場觀點高度分化</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">看好者預計泡泡瑪特今年盈利將達到165億至170億元人民幣；看淡者則預計盈利增長疲軟，且從今年下半年開始下滑。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-37d39af8-9bd9-362a-8547-dd7b6c20ac1e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行提到，投資者聚焦於即將發布的業績指引，但估計管理層的展望影響可能有限，因為看好或看淡雙方可能對同一訊息作出不同解讀。該行預計泡泡瑪特於去年第四季和今年首季在中國的銷售勢頭強勁，在供應大幅增加後，Labubu去年末季銷售表現穩健，與去年第三季水平相近。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外，市場預測泡泡瑪特受惠於去年第四季新品熱度高，如星星人等產品推動，泡泡瑪特曾指去年集團全IP全品類產品全球銷售逾4億隻，綜合券商預測，泡泡瑪特去年純利介乎108億至140.9億元人民幣，按年大增2.46倍至3.51倍。</p></div>",
